{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/node\/findchildren(pattern:type:recursive:owned:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Finds descendants of this node whose name matches "},{"code":"pattern","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String\/match(expr:)"},{"type":"text","text":", and\/or type matches "},{"code":"type","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as in "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Object\/isClass(_:)","type":"reference"},{"text":". Internal children are also searched over (see ","type":"text"},{"code":"internal","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter in ","type":"text"},{"code":"addChild(node:forceReadableName:`internal`:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Node\/findChildren(pattern:type:recursive:owned:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"findChildren"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"pattern","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"type"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":" = \"\", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"recursive","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":" = true, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"owned"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" = true) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/S